SIMPLE: stinkpot
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stinkpot
<hw>Stink"pot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
earthen jar charged with powder, grenades, and other materials of an
offensive and suffocating smell, -- sometimes used in boarding an
enemy's vessel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A vessel in which disinfectants are
burned.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The musk turtle, or musk
tortoise. See under <er>Musk</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stinkstone</ent>⟦br⟧
